# Keep internal & working documents OUT of the published repository.
# Note: .gitignore only works with git / GitHub Desktop — it does NOT block
# manual drag-and-drop uploads on the GitHub website. For manual uploads,
# only ever drag the app files (index.html and patient-portal.html).

*.md
!README.md
*.docx
*.pdf
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
